      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JETSON (8) was a last start winner (22.81) from Box 2 at this track. Boasts two wins from five starts out of this box. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. SOLO MAN (4) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (26.01) at Murray Bridge over 455m. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Expected to feature again. JUST JOHNNIE (2) was game in defeat when finished in the minors last start over the 400m at this track, running a decent 23.08 in a Other. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. MY MATE ROBBIE (1) scored with plenty to spare last time. Big chance on that form.",
